                                </li>
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        <li>
                                    <a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Left on hold: the healthcare staff who answered Ireland’s call&amp;url=https://www.independent.ie/irish-news/left-on-hold-the-healthcare-staff-who-answered-irelands-call-39336288.html" aria-label="Twitter" target="_blank" class="icon-twitter" rel="external" data-vars-category="Content Link" data-vars-action="Share" data-vars-label="Share Inline|Twitter"><span>Twitter</span></a>
